Subject: [PATCH 02/54] ARM: OMAP2+: hwmod: Fix updating of sysconfig register

[ Upstream commit 3ca4a238106dedc285193ee47f494a6584b6fd2f ]

Commit 127500ccb766f ("ARM: OMAP2+: Only write the sysconfig on idle
